caption:
Stop by for @metropolitanbakery bread and pastries, baked fresh daily! Weekend specials: Saturday Canelés & Sat/Sun Kouign Amann (availability at our Reading Terminal Market store only). 

Need your bread sliced? Just let us know, we’ll happily slice it for you on our bread slicer.

We look forward to seeing you soon!
